## Impact & Legacy  

Dr. Greg Carr's scholarship and activism have significantly influenced contemporary discussions on Black identity, education, and empowerment. His commitment to African-centered education and his leadership within Africana Studies continue to inspire students, scholars, and activists worldwide.

**Africana Studies Relation:**  
